OL,3,CNorth Wales police detective charged
OL,4,Cwith sex offence
OL,6,FA North Wales Police detective has
OL,7,Fbeen charged with operating equipment
OL,8,Funderneath clothing without consent.
OL,10,FThe force says Detective Constable
OL,11,FHarshey-Jones has been suspended from
OL,12,Fduties following an incident in the
OL,13,FColwyn Bay area earlier this month.
OL,15,FHe was charged with the offence of
OL,16,Foperating equipment beneath clothing
OL,17,Fwithout consent, in relation to the
OL,18,Fincident on 11 June.
