OL,3,CNorth Wales police detective charged
OL,4,Cwith sex offence
OL,6,FOperating equipment beneath clothing
OL,7,Fwithout consent is an offence under
OL,8,Fthe Sexual Offences Act 2003.
OL,10,FHe was subsequently remanded to appear
OL,11,Fin court on 16 June and was granted
OL,12,Fbail.
OL,14,FHe is next due to appear in Chester
OL,15,FCrown Court for a plea hearing on 14
OL,16,FJuly.
